717871f-a.title: Manhattan: Broome Street - Centre Street
717871f-a.text:
Broome Street, south side, east from Centre Street, to and including
Centre Market Place. Shown on the extreme right, is the Central Headquarters
of the New York Police Department. Note the Broome Street Tabernacle at the
S.E. corner of Centre Market Place.
April 19, 1935.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
